title: Practical Electronics Handbook [Sinclair&Dunton] PDF
description:
Practical Electronics Handbook, 6th Ed.
Ian Sinclair & John Dunton
Newnes (2007)
PDF


Practical Electronics Handbook combines a wealth useful day-to-day electronics information, concise explanations and practical guidance in this essential companion to anyone involved in electronics design and construction. The compact collection of key data, fundamental principles and circuit design basics provides an ideal reference for a wide range of students, enthusiasts, technicians and practitioners of electronics who have progressed beyond the basics.
The sixth edition is updated throughout with new material on microcontrollers and computer assistance, and a new chapter on digital signal processing

- Invaluable handbook and reference for hobbyists, students and technicians
- Essential day-to-day electronics information, clear explanations and practical guidance in one compact volume
- Assumes some previous electronics knowledge but coverage to interest beginners and professionals alike
